Subdirectories:
---------------

main       main programs mcSim.cpp and mdSim.cpp for MC and MD simulation
mcMd       classes for Monte Carlo (MC) / molecular dynamics (MD) simulation
ddMd       classes for domain-decomposition parallel MD (experimental)
inter      classes that define interaction potential energy functions
util       utility classes for scientific computation
modules    add-on components for particular applications
test       simple unit test framework
dox        source files for the html manual pages
draft      unfinished or proposed classes

Files:
------

makefile      main makefile
compiler.mk_r compiler settings (compiler and options) (default version)
LICENSE       GPL license

For compilation instructions, see the file src/dox/compile.dox, or the README 
file in the root directory (the parent of this directory).
